msg: Initial release of some experimental ontology processing utilities

msg: Added the capability of listing the restrictions that mention a given OntProperty

author: ian_dickinson
msg: Added a test for user requested behaviour (use of null's in OntModel.createIndividual), and removed obsolete test of deprecated API call.

author: ian_dickinson
msg: Fixes to listing properties in an ontology model. Clarified the contract in listOntProperties, added extra documentation. Added
listAllOntProperties() method with alternative algorithm (more robust to absence of reasoner, but slower).

author: ian_dickinson
msg: Documentation tweaks. Also added method to drop an individual from the (asserted) extension of a class.
